Hi David,

A vanagon westy seat base will also fit into a baywindow... I put one  
in my Westfakia in 2001. You will have to chisel or cut it from the  
donor bus... that took me about 5 minutes with an angle grinder.

http://www.pottsfamily.ca/westfakia/creation/pictures/agf00011.html
http://www.pottsfamily.ca/westfakia/creation/pictures/agf00012.html

